casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Metcalf.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Metcalf (1987), 31 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

(D.R. No. 87-4 Decided May 28, 1987.)

The resignation of Randall F. Metcalf as an attorney is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
